WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:05.970
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:06.480 --> 00:00:11.040
♪I've been searching for the past♪

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:17.480
♪This world and the face
that looks like yours♪

00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:22.799
♪When I start to write♪

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:29.480
♪I realize I'm slowly
walking into danger♪

00:00:29.520 --> 00:00:36.320
♪I thought it was destined loneliness♪

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:43.120
♪Through lifetimes of pain,
the memory stays clear♪

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:50.479
♪You again and again, me step by step♪

00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:56.960
♪Lost on the road searching for you♪

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:04.800
=A Fleeting Dream=

00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:08.360
=Episode 8=

00:01:08.799 --> 00:01:12.919
Everyone must have already
heard about Xinya's situation.

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:15.798
This is a turbulent time
for the Lian family.

00:01:15.799 --> 00:01:19.239
So we must choose who will take
the lead of the Lian family.

00:01:20.279 --> 00:01:22.879
No one is more qualified to be
the head of the Lian family

00:01:22.880 --> 00:01:25.000
than Miss Xinruo.

00:01:25.160 --> 00:01:27.838
Yes, I choose Miss Xinruo.

00:01:27.839 --> 00:01:28.598
Agreed.

00:01:28.599 --> 00:01:31.559
Thank you for your support.
I will do my best for the Lian family...

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:34.558
Not so fast. She's not qualified to be
the head of the Lian family.

00:01:34.559 --> 00:01:36.479
She's not even one of the Lian family.

00:01:48.480 --> 00:01:49.759
You're nothing but a fraud!

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:51.559
You're not the real Miss Xinruo!

00:01:55.480 --> 00:01:56.919
Yao uncovered evidence

00:01:56.920 --> 00:01:59.840
proving Miss Du's identity is fake.

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:01.758
To protect the Lian family's assets,

00:02:01.759 --> 00:02:03.999
I have no choice
but to reveal this will.

00:02:07.400 --> 00:02:10.919
Everyone knows Mr. Lian had
only one daughter, Xinya.

00:02:10.920 --> 00:02:12.879
Mr. Lian feared that
if something happened to him,

00:02:12.880 --> 00:02:15.278
Xinya wouldn't be able to manage
the entire family,

00:02:15.279 --> 00:02:18.038
so he prepared this will for me

00:02:18.039 --> 00:02:21.599
to temporarily oversee the Lian family.

00:02:27.079 --> 00:02:30.318
I didn't want
to present this will either,

00:02:30.319 --> 00:02:32.439
but the Lian family

00:02:32.440 --> 00:02:36.118
cannot fall
into the hands of an outsider.

00:02:36.119 --> 00:02:39.199
I must honor Mr. Lian's last wishes.

00:02:39.480 --> 00:02:42.240
Any objections?

00:02:54.380 --> 00:02:57.380
(Pei Residence)

00:02:58.799 --> 00:02:59.799
Stop right there.

00:03:00.799 --> 00:03:03.078
We had a deal.

00:03:03.079 --> 00:03:04.599
You betrayed me.

00:03:05.119 --> 00:03:07.838
Miss Du, you're far too naive.

00:03:07.839 --> 00:03:09.838
As the next head of the Pei family,

00:03:09.839 --> 00:03:11.798
all of its assets belong to me.

00:03:11.799 --> 00:03:13.399
Why would I ever abandon the Pei family

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:14.880
to work with you?

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:17.479
I've heard all about you.

00:03:17.480 --> 00:03:20.758
Your father was only the secretary
to the Lian family head back then.

00:03:20.759 --> 00:03:22.118
Shortly after the head died,

00:03:22.119 --> 00:03:24.479
you abandoned Lian Xinruo

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.720
and quickly went after Pei Xueshan.

00:03:27.039 --> 00:03:28.558
You don't love anyone.

00:03:28.558 --> 00:03:30.879
Everyone around you is just
a stepping stone to climb higher...

00:03:30.880 --> 00:03:32.800
Lian family and I share
a blood feud over my father's death!

00:03:32.800 --> 00:03:34.318
How could I possibly stay with Xinruo?

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:38.399
My feelings for Xinruo
have never changed.

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:41.240
You don't deserve to even say her name.

00:03:41.559 --> 00:03:44.999
That proves you never
cared about Pei Xueshan.

00:03:50.799 --> 00:03:52.318
You're free to mock me all you want.

00:03:52.319 --> 00:03:53.758
But after today,

00:03:53.759 --> 00:03:56.599
I doubt you can even stay in Hu City.

00:03:56.759 --> 00:03:58.759
We'll see

00:03:59.599 --> 00:04:01.239
about that.

00:04:06.480 --> 00:04:07.639
Since you returned

00:04:07.640 --> 00:04:09.479
to the country,

00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:10.879
all you've done is rest at home

00:04:10.880 --> 00:04:13.159
or make merry with Miss Du.

00:04:13.160 --> 00:04:15.078
I almost forgot

00:04:15.079 --> 00:04:16.118
when you were young,

00:04:16.119 --> 00:04:20.360
our father and the elder clan members
praised you as clever beyond your years,

00:04:20.599 --> 00:04:23.999
the perfect candidate to be family head.

00:04:25.839 --> 00:04:27.519
What do you mean by that?

00:04:30.119 --> 00:04:33.679
I never doubted you were smart.

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:35.879
You must have seen through

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:37.800
Miss Du's identity all along.

00:04:37.920 --> 00:04:41.760
So all this time you've been
supporting her behind the scenes.

00:04:42.319 --> 00:04:44.239
If Youmeng wants something,

00:04:44.559 --> 00:04:46.399
I'll help her get it.

00:04:46.559 --> 00:04:48.278
What Du Youmeng wants?

00:04:48.279 --> 00:04:50.038
Or what you want?

00:04:50.039 --> 00:04:52.999
Why beat around the bush?

00:04:55.559 --> 00:04:57.559
That's a strange thing to say.

00:04:57.599 --> 00:04:59.479
You acquired the Lian family's assets

00:04:59.759 --> 00:05:02.199
through less than honest methods.

00:05:02.759 --> 00:05:04.839
Everyone's just using their own skills.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.999
The blood running through the Pei family

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:15.040
is that of acquisitors.

00:05:15.119 --> 00:05:17.439
I might let this slide this time,

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:19.758
but Du Youmeng must leave the Pei family

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:21.119
and Hu City.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.080
That's not happening.

00:05:26.640 --> 00:05:30.200
Yuze, don't test my patience.

00:05:30.440 --> 00:05:31.800
Don't worry.

00:05:33.079 --> 00:05:34.959
I don't intend to make an enemy of you.

00:05:35.160 --> 00:05:36.680
My time is limited.

00:05:37.119 --> 00:05:39.239
I just want to be with the one I love.

00:05:40.480 --> 00:05:43.760
Now that you have the Lian family,

00:05:43.839 --> 00:05:45.759
please stop making things hard
for Youmeng.

00:05:53.440 --> 00:05:56.038
I didn't expect Lian Xinya
would be silenced so quickly.

00:05:56.039 --> 00:05:59.079
They act without any scruples.

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:04.000
Because they've never had
to pay for their crimes.

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:09.160
Now is not the right time

00:06:09.680 --> 00:06:11.360
to reclaim the Lian family.

00:06:12.359 --> 00:06:13.639
Don't be hasty.

00:06:13.759 --> 00:06:15.399
I've come to realize,

00:06:15.640 --> 00:06:17.598
whether I am Lian Xinruo or not,

00:06:17.599 --> 00:06:20.118
Pei Yujie is determined
to seize the Lian family.

00:06:20.119 --> 00:06:22.479
You stopped me from continuing
to oppose him today

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:24.000
because you're worried about me.

00:06:24.119 --> 00:06:25.479
You're worried he might target me

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:29.240
and make it harder for me to track down
leads about my father's disappearance.

00:06:29.519 --> 00:06:31.439
Lian Xinya didn't know
the truth about your father.

00:06:31.900 --> 00:06:34.080
You'll need to find an opportunity
to meet with Lian Zhong.

00:06:35.240 --> 00:06:36.679
The problem is,

00:06:36.680 --> 00:06:38.758
I've confronted Pei Yujie many times.

00:06:38.759 --> 00:06:40.559
Won't he come after me too?

00:06:40.720 --> 00:06:42.720
Then let him hesitate to make a move

00:06:43.640 --> 00:06:45.640
and think twice
before acting against you.

00:06:50.880 --> 00:06:52.640
It's time to make use

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.760
of your identity as a singer, Meng Die.

00:06:56.460 --> 00:06:59.460
(Meng Die, gorgeous,
captivating, stunning red lips)

00:07:01.039 --> 00:07:02.118
(Latest reports.)

00:07:02.119 --> 00:07:04.639
(People's Daily)
(Singer Du Youmeng releases new single.)

00:07:04.640 --> 00:07:07.160
(The record sold out instantly
upon release.)

00:07:07.359 --> 00:07:10.479
(She is to collaborate
with a renowned perfume brand.)

00:07:10.759 --> 00:07:12.278
(Baohua Film Company reveals)

00:07:12.279 --> 00:07:14.278
(they're actively inviting
Miss Du Youmeng)

00:07:14.279 --> 00:07:16.559
(to star in the movie, "Goddess' Ode.")

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:20.078
My brother is impressive.

00:07:20.079 --> 00:07:21.639
In just one month,

00:07:21.640 --> 00:07:24.399
he's made Du Youmeng
Hu City's top celebrity.

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:27.040
She's just a lowly performer,
nothing more.

00:07:27.319 --> 00:07:28.919
Don't pay her any mind.

00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:31.680
Master Pei!

00:07:33.519 --> 00:07:36.479
There are a lot of reporters outside
blocking the front gate.

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:38.199
They're all here to interview Miss Du.

00:07:38.200 --> 00:07:39.839
This is unacceptable.

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:40.758
Send them all away.

00:07:40.759 --> 00:07:41.839
Yes, sir.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:44.319
Master Pei.

00:07:44.320 --> 00:07:45.439
What now?

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:47.239
The Commanding Officer's wife

00:07:47.240 --> 00:07:48.800
just sent a formal visit request.

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:53.399
Tell the butler to prepare for her visit.
She must be received with the highest honor.

00:07:53.400 --> 00:07:54.480
Yes, sir.

00:07:56.079 --> 00:07:57.879
The Hu City Commander is always aloof.

00:07:57.880 --> 00:07:59.838
He never mingles with merchants.

00:07:59.839 --> 00:08:01.999
For his wife
to visit us all of a sudden,

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:03.639
could they want to foster ties with us?

00:08:03.640 --> 00:08:05.598
Yao, go change.

00:08:05.599 --> 00:08:06.879
We'll greet them together.

00:08:06.880 --> 00:08:07.920
Understood.

00:08:10.240 --> 00:08:11.999
Madam.

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:14.080
Welcome, welcome...

00:08:14.880 --> 00:08:16.200
Miss Du.

00:08:16.359 --> 00:08:17.919
We meet at least.

00:08:17.920 --> 00:08:18.799
My daughter and I

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:20.359
are both your fans.

00:08:20.600 --> 00:08:22.758
I heard you're releasing a new single.

00:08:22.759 --> 00:08:24.519
When will the album come out?

00:08:24.520 --> 00:08:26.399
Yes, when's the release date?

00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:27.999
Ladies, be patient.

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:29.158
Let's go inside and talk.

00:08:29.159 --> 00:08:30.238
- Of course.
- All right.

00:08:30.239 --> 00:08:31.119
Please.

00:08:47.880 --> 00:08:48.759
My daughter knew

00:08:48.760 --> 00:08:50.198
I was coming today.

00:08:50.199 --> 00:08:52.239
She insisted I bring along

00:08:52.279 --> 00:08:54.039
a case of "Keke Cola."

00:08:54.960 --> 00:08:57.399
She said since you returned from abroad,

00:08:57.400 --> 00:08:58.599
you must love this drink.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:09:01.879
Young folks are the only ones
who like these newfangled things.

00:09:01.880 --> 00:09:03.479
I'm not used to drinking that.

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:04.999
That's very thoughtful of you.

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:05.919
Next time

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:08.638
I'll bring my new album over
to visit you.

00:09:08.639 --> 00:09:09.999
That would be wonderful.

00:09:10.159 --> 00:09:11.199
Here.

00:09:13.040 --> 00:09:13.879
Oh, my.

00:09:13.880 --> 00:09:17.040
Second Master and Miss Du
are such a loving couple.

00:09:17.319 --> 00:09:20.198
This is the first time I've seen a woman
playing mahjong with a man

00:09:20.199 --> 00:09:21.999
waiting on her hand and foot.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:23.520
Madam Hou, you tease us.

00:09:24.319 --> 00:09:25.879
I'm just a carefree soul

00:09:25.920 --> 00:09:27.758
who can only
take care of my lover at home.

00:09:27.759 --> 00:09:30.399
I can't compare
to the well-known Mr. Hou.

00:09:30.400 --> 00:09:32.838
No matter how much praise
he gets outside,

00:09:32.839 --> 00:09:35.639
at home he's still a clueless,
unsentimental blockhead.

00:09:35.920 --> 00:09:38.280
He hasn't a single romantic bone.

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:40.240
Take it from someone who's been around.

00:09:40.319 --> 00:09:43.919
You two are young.
Get married soon and have a child.

00:09:43.920 --> 00:09:45.239
That's what really matters.

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:46.278
Eight bamboo.

00:09:46.279 --> 00:09:47.599
That's right.

00:09:47.600 --> 00:09:50.840
Ever since my husband took a concubine,

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:52.838
he hasn't even touched me.

00:09:52.839 --> 00:09:53.799
Red.

00:09:54.159 --> 00:09:55.039
I'll take that.

00:09:56.199 --> 00:09:57.759
I'll go get some more soda.

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:01.999
Ladies, you don't know this.

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:03.678
Yuze's health

00:10:03.679 --> 00:10:05.238
hasn't been great lately,

00:10:05.239 --> 00:10:06.838
and he's on medicine.

00:10:06.839 --> 00:10:08.919
Men and their pride.

00:10:08.920 --> 00:10:10.600
Please don't tease him too much.

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:14.999
No laughing.

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:16.278
Look at me.

00:10:16.279 --> 00:10:17.638
I really should mind my tongue.

00:10:17.639 --> 00:10:18.519
Enough of that.

00:10:18.520 --> 00:10:19.680
Let's get back to the game.

00:10:20.759 --> 00:10:21.919
I win!

00:10:22.319 --> 00:10:23.318
Oh, my.

00:10:23.319 --> 00:10:25.318
Look at her tiles.

00:10:25.319 --> 00:10:26.758
She's so lucky.

00:10:26.759 --> 00:10:29.678
My luck's good today.

00:10:29.679 --> 00:10:31.278
Butler, get the car ready!

00:10:31.279 --> 00:10:32.599
I'm heading out!

00:11:13.400 --> 00:11:15.600
Uncle Zhong, it's me.

00:11:15.880 --> 00:11:17.798
You must know who I am by now.

00:11:17.799 --> 00:11:19.198
I'll ask you a few questions.

00:11:19.199 --> 00:11:20.999
Blink once for yes.

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:22.520
Twice for no.

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:27.520
Is my father dead?

00:11:31.880 --> 00:11:33.439
Did you kill him?

00:11:38.359 --> 00:11:38.959
Then who did it?

00:11:38.960 --> 00:11:40.520
Was it Pei Yujie?

00:11:44.400 --> 00:11:46.520
Yujie. Yujie!

00:12:14.960 --> 00:12:16.360
All right, Peirong.

00:12:16.440 --> 00:12:17.640
Talk.

00:12:17.839 --> 00:12:20.399
I was going to have my men
quietly take care of Lian Zhong.

00:12:20.560 --> 00:12:23.638
But a woman showed up.

00:12:23.639 --> 00:12:25.198
My men didn't know their limits

00:12:25.199 --> 00:12:26.039
and used a knife.

00:12:26.040 --> 00:12:27.640
We'll have to come up with a story

00:12:28.199 --> 00:12:30.718
to explain Lian Zhong's cause of death.

00:12:30.719 --> 00:12:32.079
A woman?

00:12:32.400 --> 00:12:33.638
She had her face covered,

00:12:33.639 --> 00:12:35.319
and the room was pitch black.

00:12:35.560 --> 00:12:38.000
But my men said

00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:42.439
her silhouette resembled Du Youmeng.

00:12:42.440 --> 00:12:43.800
Du Youmeng?

00:12:43.839 --> 00:12:45.239
(Du Youmeng?)

00:12:48.719 --> 00:12:50.158
Du Youmeng wouldn't be interested

00:12:50.159 --> 00:12:54.359
in Lian Zhong who's lost value to them.

00:12:55.400 --> 00:12:56.720
But Lian Xinruo

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:58.920
is a different matter.

00:13:00.880 --> 00:13:04.198
Yujie, you mean Du Youmeng

00:13:04.199 --> 00:13:06.119
is Lian Xinruo?

00:13:07.480 --> 00:13:09.720
I can't be certain yet.

00:13:12.239 --> 00:13:13.278
Don't worry.

00:13:13.279 --> 00:13:16.879
That woman was stabbed on her right arm.

00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:18.999
Even if we don't catch anyone today,

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:22.120
we need only examine her arm tomorrow.

00:13:23.960 --> 00:13:25.960
If it really was Lian Xinruo,

00:13:26.159 --> 00:13:28.719
then she must have come
looking for Lian Zhong

00:13:29.440 --> 00:13:31.678
about Lian Chen's death.

00:13:31.679 --> 00:13:34.399
Lian Zhong can't speak anymore.

00:13:34.400 --> 00:13:36.280
What could she even find out?

00:13:36.440 --> 00:13:38.920
No one but you and me

00:13:39.040 --> 00:13:42.480
knows Lian Chen is dead,

00:13:42.520 --> 00:13:48.360
and no one knows it was us who killed
Lian Chen and Jiang Mingcheng.

00:13:52.660 --> 00:13:54.980
(Pei Residence)

00:14:24.080 --> 00:14:25.280
What happened?

00:14:25.679 --> 00:14:27.239
Lian Zhong confessed.

00:14:28.799 --> 00:14:30.999
Pei Yujie killed my father.

00:14:34.359 --> 00:14:36.759
I stopped hoping a long time ago.

00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:40.640
But when I heard him admit it,

00:14:43.080 --> 00:14:45.040
I just couldn't help it...

00:14:51.839 --> 00:14:53.199
Cry it out.

00:14:53.520 --> 00:14:54.920
You'll feel better.

00:14:58.759 --> 00:14:59.759
No.

00:15:00.960 --> 00:15:03.040
The most important thing now

00:15:03.440 --> 00:15:05.960
is to find my father's body.

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:08.160
I must avenge him.

00:15:08.560 --> 00:15:09.800
Don't worry.

00:15:11.719 --> 00:15:13.199
I'll help you.

00:15:14.780 --> 00:15:18.238
(Pei Residence)

00:15:18.239 --> 00:15:19.959
Master! Master!

00:15:19.960 --> 00:15:21.880
Look who's here!

00:15:23.560 --> 00:15:25.160
Police investigation.

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:28.599
Chief Wu, what's with the big operation

00:15:28.600 --> 00:15:30.240
this early in the morning?

00:15:30.520 --> 00:15:32.999
(Police)
Mr. Lian Zhong was murdered last night.

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:35.120
According to eyewitness accounts,

00:15:35.639 --> 00:15:39.959
the attacker resembled Miss Du.

00:15:41.679 --> 00:15:43.358
Chief Wu, do you have any evidence?

00:15:43.359 --> 00:15:44.520
Of course.

00:15:45.120 --> 00:15:47.840
The killer was wounded
on the right arm last night.

00:15:47.920 --> 00:15:51.079
If Miss Du allows us to examine her arm,

00:15:51.080 --> 00:15:53.960
the truth will come out.

00:15:57.120 --> 00:15:59.758
Miss Du, I believe you're innocent.

00:15:59.759 --> 00:16:02.238
But Chief Wu is just doing his job.

00:16:02.239 --> 00:16:05.599
Please cooperate.

00:16:10.839 --> 00:16:11.960
Absolutely not.

00:16:11.960 --> 00:16:14.840
You don't even have any evidence and
you're dragging her name through the mud.

00:16:14.840 --> 00:16:15.599
Yuze is right.

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:17.880
I have a reputation in Hu City.

00:16:17.920 --> 00:16:19.479
If I let you check my arm,

00:16:19.480 --> 00:16:21.238
how can I face anyone if this leaks out?

